body_mass.description: The mass of specimen having the trait.

body_mass_ambiguous.description: Specifies if the recorded body mass is ambiguous.

body_mass_units_inferred.description: Specifies if the body mass units were inferred.

countryCode.description: The country where the specimen with the trait was found.

day.description: The day of the month that the trait was recorded.

decimalLatitude.description: The latitude where the specimen with the trait was found.

decimalLongitude.description: The longitude where the specimen with the trait was found.

ear_from_notch.description: Length of the ear from the notch to the tip.

ear_length.description: The length of an external ear.

ear_length_units_inferred.description: Specifies if the ear length units were inferred.

embryo_count.description: The number of embryos observed in uterus.

embryo_size_units_inferred.description: Specifies if the embryo size units were inferred.

hind_foot_length_units_inferred.description: Specifies if the hind foot length units were inferred.

hind_foot_with_claw.description: A length measurement of a hindfoot that includes the nail.

lactation.description: Secretion or expression of milk from the mammary glands.

life_stage.description: The developmental stage of the life cycle of the organism represented.

month.description: The month that the trait was recorded.

nipple.description: The morphology of the specimen's nipple(s).

nipple_count.description: The number of nipples the specimen has.

occurrenceID.description: Identifies the record that contains the trait data values.

pregnancy.description: The specimen's uterus contains a developing embryo, fetus, or unborn offspring.

sex.description: The biological sex of the specimen.

stateProvince.description: The state where the specimen with the trait was found.

tail_length.description: The length of the specimen's tail.

tail_length_estimated.description: Specifies if the tail length was estimated.

tail_length_units_inferred.description: Specifies if the tail length units were inferred.

testicle_length.description: The length of the long axis of testis spheroid.

testicle_size_units_inferred.description: Specifies if the testis size units were inferred.

testicle_width.description: The length of the short axis of testis spheroid (perpendicular to long axis at midpoint).

total_length.description: Total length of the specimen. Fish:Total length (TL) is the length of a fish measured from the tip of the snout to tip of the longest lobe of caudal fin. Measurement done with caudal fin lobes compressed and measured at midline.

total_length_ambiguous.description: Specifies if the total length recorded is ambiguous.

total_length_estimated.description: Specifies if the total length was estimated.

total_length_units_inferred.description: Specifies if the total length units were inferred.

tragus_length.description: The length of the specimen's tragus.

vagina.description: The degree of perforation of the female vagina.

year.description: The year that the trait was recorded.
